    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a remarkably well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, with the original paint holding a deep luster, complemented by clean alloy wheels and clear headlamp lenses. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the upholstery is free of tears or heavy stains, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and provides a composed, quiet ride on the highway. We have maintained a detailed log of all oil changes and preventative maintenance, ensuring the engine and transmission remain in top form. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with its age, the overall presentation is sharp and professional. This is a dependable, high-quality driver\u2019s car that is ready for many more miles of reliable service.",
